---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <section style="padding-top: 60px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="margin-left: 0; max-width: var(--container);">
            <span class="tag sanskrit">॥ कर्मण्येवाधिकारस्ते ॥</span>
            <span class="tag">Services</span>
            <h1>Work With <span class="highlight">Aman</span></h1>
            <p class="lead" style="max-width: 650px;">
                Systems become more important as complexity increases. I help professionals and organizations create clearer digital presence, knowledge, and operational systems.
            </p>
            <p style="max-width: 600px; color: var(--text-muted);">
                <strong style="color: var(--text);">Every engagement begins with understanding.</strong>
                Not with solutions. Before recommendations, implementation, or optimization, I start by examining the system itself.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding-top: 20px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="services-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;">

                <!-- Systems Audit -->
                <div class="service-card" style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <span class="badge" style="display: inline-block; font-size: 0.55rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent-dim); padding: 0.1rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Audit</span>
                    <h3>Systems Audit</h3>
                    <div class="price-tag" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin: 0.5rem 0 0.2rem 0;">₹4,999</div>
                    <div class="timeline" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;">Timeline: 7 Business Days</div>
                    <ul class="deliverables" style="list-style: none; margin: 0.5rem 0 1.2rem 0; flex: 1;">
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">Comprehensive Systems Audit Report</li>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">Prioritized Recommendations</li>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: none;">60-Minute Review Session</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="card-footer" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 0.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">
                        <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;">Not every application is accepted</span>
                        <a href="/work-with-aman/systems-audit" class="know-more" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">Know More <span style="transition: transform 0.2s;">→</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Digital Presence Systems -->
                <div class="service-card" style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <span class="badge" style="display: inline-block; font-size: 0.55rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent-dim); padding: 0.1rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Digital Presence</span>
                    <h3>Digital Presence Systems</h3>
                    <div class="price-tag" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin: 0.5rem 0 0.2rem 0;">Starting at ₹25,000</div>
                    <div class="timeline" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;">Timeline: 2–4 Weeks</div>
                    <ul class="deliverables" style="list-style: none; margin: 0.5rem 0 1.2rem 0; flex: 1;">
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">Digital Presence Audit</li>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">Website Architecture</li>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: none;">Navigation &amp; Content Framework</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="card-footer" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 0.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">
                        <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;">Systems Audit Included</span>
                        <a href="/work-with-aman/digital-presence" class="know-more" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">Know More <span style="transition: transform 0.2s;">→</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Knowledge Systems -->
                <div class="service-card" style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <span class="badge" style="display: inline-block; font-size: 0.55rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent-dim); padding: 0.1rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Knowledge</span>
                    <h3>Knowledge Systems</h3>
                    <div class="price-tag" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin: 0.5rem 0 0.2rem 0;">Starting at ₹35,000</div>
                    <div class="timeline" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;">Timeline: 2–4 Weeks</div>
                    <ul class="deliverables" style="list-style: none; margin: 0.5rem 0 1.2rem 0; flex: 1;">
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">Knowledge Audit</li>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">Knowledge Architecture</li>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: none;">Documentation Framework</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="card-footer" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 0.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">
                        <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;">Systems Audit Included</span>
                        <a href="/work-with-aman/knowledge-systems" class="know-more" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">Know More <span style="transition: transform 0.2s;">→</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Business Systems & Automation -->
                <div class="service-card" style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <span class="badge" style="display: inline-block; font-size: 0.55rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent-dim); padding: 0.1rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Operations</span>
                    <h3>Business Systems &amp; Automation</h3>
                    <div class="price-tag" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin: 0.5rem 0 0.2rem 0;">Starting at ₹50,000</div>
                    <div class="timeline" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;">Timeline: 4–8 Weeks</div>
                    <ul class="deliverables" style="list-style: none; margin: 0.5rem 0 1.2rem 0; flex: 1;">
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">Workflow Audit</li>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">Process Architecture</li>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: none;">Lead &amp; Onboarding Systems</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="card-footer" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 0.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--grid-line);">
                        <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;">Systems Audit Included</span>
                        <a href="/work-with-aman/business-systems" class="know-more" style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">Know More <span style="transition: transform 0.2s;">→</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding-top: 60px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 3rem;" />
            <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 2rem;">
                <div>
                    <span class="tag sanskrit">॥ सत्यमेव जयते ॥</span>
                    <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">Start With <span class="highlight">Understanding</span></h2>
                    <p style="max-width: 500px;">
                        Most problems hide behind other problems. Before changing software tools, redesigning workflows, or investing in automation, it helps to understand what is actually happening beneath the surface.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <a href="/work-with-aman/systems-audit" class="btn">Request a Systems Audit</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>